    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated garlic</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>peri-peri spice mix </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>tomato paste</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant – this is your <strong>peri-peri tomato mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
