    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>peri-peri tomato mix</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>mayo </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and mix until fully combined (reserve the pan!) – this is your <strong>perinaise</strong></p>",
