    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate pot on a medium heat with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once hot,<strong> </strong>add the <strong>blanched peas </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1-2 min or until they're warmed through</p><p>Once warmed through, add the <strong>chopped mint </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>punchy peas</strong></p>",
